================================================================================
1. PROJECT OVERVIEW
================================================================================

Package Name: @alidplus/uikit
Version: 0.2.0
Type: React Component Library (TypeScript)
Framework: React 18/19
Styling: SCSS Modules + CSS Variables
Build Tool: Vite
Variant System: Class Variance Authority (CVA)

This is a comprehensive UI component library built with React and TypeScript.
It provides a complete design system with:
- 35+ reusable components
- Design tokens for colors, spacing, typography
- Dark mode support
- Responsive design utilities
- Icon library integration

================================================================================
2. INSTALLATION & SETUP
================================================================================

INSTALLATION:
npm install @alidplus/uikit

PEER DEPENDENCIES:
- react: ^18.0.0 || ^19.0.0
- react-dom: ^18.0.0 || ^19.0.0

IMPORT STYLES:
Import the CSS file in your main entry point:
import '@alidplus/uikit/style.css';

OR import variables:
import '@alidplus/uikit/variables.scss';

IMPORT COMPONENTS:
// Import all components
import { Button, Input, Card, Modal } from '@alidplus/uikit';

// Or import specific components
import { Button } from '@alidplus/uikit/buttons';
import { Input } from '@alidplus/uikit/input';

IMPORT ICONS:
import { CheckCircle, DangerCircle } from '@alidplus/uikit/icons';

