================================================================================
5. SHARED UTILITIES
================================================================================

5.1 SHARED VARIANTS
------------------

All components that support shared variants can use:

- rounded: 'none' | 'xxs' | 'xs' | 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg' | 'xl' | 'xxl' | 'xxxl' | 'rounded'
- pad: 'none' | 'xs' | 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg' | 'xl'
- gap: 'none' | 'xs' | 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg' | 'xl'
- level: 'none' | 'xs' | 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg' | 'xl' (shadow)
- border: 'none' | '1' | '2' | '3' | '4' | '5'
- flex: 'vertical' | 'horizontal' | 'center'
- variant: 'primary' (for some components)

USAGE:
<Button
  rounded="md"
  pad="md"
  level="sm"
  border="1"
>
  Button
</Button>

5.2 TYPES
--------

Common TypeScript interfaces:

- IOptionValue<T>: For dropdown/select options
  - value: T
  - label?: string
  - icon?: ReactNode
  - text?: string
  - disabled?: boolean
  - onClick?: VoidFunction

- DataProps<T>: Generic data prop
  - data: T

- ValueProps<T>: Generic value prop
  - value?: T

- InputProps<T>: Input with onChange
  - value?: T
  - onChange: Dispatch<SetStateAction<T>>

