================================================================================
9. BEST PRACTICES
================================================================================

1. Always import the CSS file first:
   import '@alidplus/uikit/style.css';

2. Use semantic color tokens instead of primitive colors:
   ✅ var(--color-text-text-primary)
   ❌ var(--color-gray-1000)

3. Use spacing tokens for consistent spacing:
   ✅ var(--spacing-spacing-md)
   ❌ 20px

4. Leverage shared variants for consistent styling:
   ✅ <Button rounded="md" pad="md" level="sm" />
   ❌ Custom inline styles

5. Use appropriate component sizes:
   - 'sm' for compact UIs
   - 'default' for standard UIs
   - 'lg' for prominent elements

6. Always provide accessible labels:
   ✅ <Input label="Email" />
   ❌ <Input placeholder="Email" />

7. Use icons from the icon library:
   ✅ import { CheckCircle } from '@alidplus/uikit/icons';
   ❌ Custom SVG icons

8. Handle dark mode properly:
   - Test components in both light and dark themes
   - Use semantic tokens that adapt automatically

